            Real Goods Solar, Inc. is a residential and commercial solar energy engineering, procurement, and construction company. It offers turnkey services, including design, procurement, permitting, build-out, grid connection, financing referrals, and warranty and customer satisfaction activities. The company was founded on January 29, 2008 and is headquartered in Louisville, CO.

            
