Real Goods Solar, Inc.





Type

Public


Traded as
NASDAQ: RGSE


Genre
Residential and commercial solar PV installation


Founded
1978


Founder
John Schaeffer


Headquarters
833 West S. Boulder Rd, Louisville, Colorado, USA



Key people

Chief Executive Officer
Dennis Lacey


Products
Renewable energy systems


Website
RealGoodsSolar.com
RGSEnergy.com


Real Goods Solar Inc. NASDAQ: RGSE is a publicly traded residential solar power integrator doing business as RGS Energy.[1] The company established its roots as a provider of sustainable lifestyle products through its retail division, dating back to 1978, when it sold some of the first retail solar panels in the United States. The company now has customers in all 50 American states and all 10 Canadian provinces.




