READ MORE TESTIMONIALS

SOLAR PRICING
 







 






A Top Rated National Solar Company Solar Installation Experience Since 1978 Solar power can actually cost less than what you pay now with a low, predictable, locked-in electricity rate. Over 25,000 customers have chosen us to bring more than 260 MW of clean, affordable solar to their homes and businesses.  





Top of the line products: More than 35 years ago, RGS Energy – a Real Goods Solar Company – sold some of the very first solar panels to the public out of a small general store in Northern California. Since then, we’ve installed over 25,000 solar energy systems for homes, businesses, schools, government facilities, and utilities across the country, totaling more than 260 megawatts of clean energy.









Unrivaled Customer Service: Ensuring the satisfaction of our customers is our top priority. If you’ve had an issue with any aspect of your solar installation, please let us know ASAP. We bring a local focus backed by decades of knowledge and experience, and we pride ourselves on acting as a community-minded solar service provider. 









Official RGS DOW Warranty: DOW announced on June 28, 2016, that it will cease manufacturing POWERHOUSE™ modules. As part of the transition to cease POWERHOUSE™ operations, DOW will no longer be providing design services or material for new projects. RGS Energy has been selected by DOW Solar to be the official warranty servicer for DOW POWERHOUSE™ systems and will continue to fully support warranties on existing POWERHOUSE™ systems.



