Solar Exposure in 10 States
From our humble beginnings in Northern California, RGS Energy now offers full-service solar panel installation and financing to 10 U.S. states (including Hawaii as Sunetric).
Good Energy is Getting Around
With more than 25,000 solar power systems installed – generating over 260 MW of renewable energy – we are one of the nation’s leading solar PV installation companies. With our extensive experience, we are confident we can make electricity from solar a cleaner, more affordable reality for most homeowners. Solar rebates and financing options vary by state. Click on your state to get details about what’s available in your area, or simply let us present your options by getting a free quote now.



